questions.quote: Ohh... Oh, that's okay I hate when people come back to complement the chef. Like I have nothing better to do! So what's up?
I'm agreeing with you. Did you, listen, did you happen to tell Phoebe yet?
Oh well, they're killing off one of the characters on the show, and when she dies her brain is being transplanted into my body.
No, we're just four people with neck problems. You talk like this.
She's really going to love this, you know? The bottom line is I want her to have it, even if I don't get to be the one who gives it to her.
Well y'know, they only give you three letters, so after A-S-S it is a bit of a challenge.
Well umm, I was thinking that maybe we could come up with a system where we trade of being maid of honor for each other. Like hypothetically, if Phoebe were mine...
No! Forget her, man! You don't need her, you don't need that!
Oh, it would be you! You! Monica! And you'd get all the votes!
Hey, honey! What's the matter? Fine, I was just trying to be nice! Whoa!
